sub_title: Working with customers to simplify & optimize their supply chains
summary:
I am a seasoned Supply Chain and Logistics professional specializing in improvement and optimization of any kind-- process, supply chain, inventory or operations in the supply chain domain. 
 
I analyze and help businesses to run their daily course optimally by identifying improvement opportunities and come up with simple but innovative solutions save cost and continue to be remain lean. I have helped big corporations identify considerable cost savings opportunities in their supply chain network through various end-to-end optimization studies and I am now focusing on helping teams optimize their processes.
 
I believe in the below three things in my personal & professional life:
 
1.	Unflinching Values
2.	Continued Learning
3.	Flexibility or Readiness to Change
 
These are the three things that guide me and keep me motivated.
 
I am a traveler by heart and love to explore new places, cultures, culinary tastes and meeting new people. An amateur photographer inclined towards wildlife and landscape photography. History,  Mythology, Sports intrigue me.
 
Specialties: Lean Six Sigma, Process Improvement, Supply Chain Management Supply Chain Analytics and Optimization, People Management, Strategic Planning, Green Logistics
